HARDWARE AND SOFTWARE SOLUTIONS FOR THE DRONE REVOLUTIONCollect and analyze high quality data – make smarter decisions faster
 
 
 
 




Products & SolutionsA drone on its own is nothing more than a remote control toy. But when connected to a complete networked support system it becomes a powerful automated business solution that helps companies make better decisions faster.

Read More

 


Industries We ServeThe commercial unmanned aerial vehicle industry is rapidly expanding. Valmie applies UAV technology to a wide variety of sectors such as oil and gas, agriculture, real estate and news reporting.

Read More

 


Invest with VisionAs more industries begin employing drones to increase efficiencies and safely obtain quality information, the time is right for investors to consider the first-mover opportunity this technology presents. If you recognize the important role drones will play in the global economy, we welcome you as an investor.

