			Company Description 


			Valmie Resources, Inc. develops aerial data collection software, hardware and cloud services for commercial applications. It focuses on pursuing opportunities for the commercialization of products and services in the technology industry. The company was founded on August 26, 2011 and is headquartere...
		


                Valmie Resources, Inc. develops aerial data collection software, hardware and cloud services for commercial applications. It focuses on pursuing opportunities for the commercialization of products and services in the technology industry. The company was founded on August 26, 2011 and is headquartered in Houston, TX.
            




