Valmie Resources, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:45 PM ET
Aerospace and Defense

Company Overview of Valmie Resources, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Valmie Resources, Inc. focuses on the development of unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) software, hardware, and cloud services for a range of commercial applications worldwide. The company offers aerial data collection hardware, software, and data storage solutions. It develops Autonomous Intelligence for Mobilized Devices (AIMD) Platform as the intersection point for real-time operational intelligence and workflow that is accessible anywhere and anytime; and V-Series UAVs, including traditional multi-rotor, and vertical takeoff and landing UAV systems. Valmie Resources, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Houston, Texas.


2603 Augusta DriveSuite 840Houston, TX 77057United StatesFounded in 20118 Employees



Phone: 713-595-6675

www.valmie.com







Key Executives for Valmie Resources, Inc.




Mr. Gerald B. Hammack


      	Chairman, CEO, President, CFO, Principal Accounting Officer, Secretary and Treasurer
      


